{"word":"H5534 - סָכַר - çâkar - saw-kar' - Stop","slug":"H5534","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">סָכַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>çâkar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>saw-kar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Stop"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E1;&#x05DB;&#x05E8; - sa&#x0302;kar</b> - <i>saw-kar'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>shut</i> up; by implication to <i>surrender</i>: - stop, give over. See also <a href=\"#/H5462\">H5462</a>; <a href=\"#/H7936\">H7936</a>."}]}